<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894868>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 50–55. SEM. F. rexii. External and internal valve views of four specimens collected in the summer of 2008. Fig. 50, Full external valve view showing the strongly rhomboid valve shape. Fig. 51, Crescent moon shaped external distal raphe end. Fig. 52, External central area showing a grouping of small poroids and the crescent moon shaped raphe endings. Fig. 53. Full internal valve view showing the robust longitudinal rib system. Fig. 54. Internal valve apex with distinct and prominent porte-crayon structure and abruptly widened longitudinal ribs. Fig. 55. Internal central area with greatly constricted longitudinal ribs. Scale bars: Figs 50, 53: 10 µm; Figs 51–52, 55: 2 µm; Fig. 54: 1 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894868/files/figure.png" .

